<body>
    <%- include('../partials/navbar')%>
        <section class="w-full  object-contain">
            <img src="../../../public/img/14.png" alt="">
        </section>
        <section class="md:flex h-full">
            <div class="p-4 md:p-8 md:w-3/5 flex flex-col justify-center items-start">
                <h1 class="my-color">About Bikram Yoga</h1>
                <h1 class="text-2xl font-semibold">What Is Bikram Yoga?</h1>
                <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm my-4">Bikram Yoga is a system of hot yoga, a type of yoga as exercise, devised by Bikram Choudhury and based on the teachings of B. C. Ghosh, that became popular in the early 1970s.
                </p>
                <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm my-4">Classes consist of a fixed sequence of 26 postures, practiced in a room heated to 105 °F (41 °C) with a humidity of 40%, intended to replicate the climate of India.
                </p>
                <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm my-4">The room is fitted with carpets and the walls are covered in mirrors. The instructor may adjust the students' yoga postures. Choudhury's teaching style was abrasive.
                </p>
                <a href="/bikram"> <button class="my-btn">Start Session</button></a>
            </div>
            <div class="p-4 md:p-8 md:w-2/5 object-cover flex flex-col justify-center items-center">
                <img src="../../../public/img/15.png" alt="">
            </div>
        </section>
